dcterms:creator: S. Petrushevski
dcterms:description: This dataset contains air pollution measurements from seven stations in Skopje, including pollutants such as CO, NO2, O3, PM10, and PM2.5. The focus of the study is on PM2.5 and the dataset originally had missing values and outliers, which were addressed through linear interpolation.
dcterms:title: Air pollution data collected in Skopje
